1. Install XAMPP

2. Start up XAMPP Control Panel

3. Start Apache and MySQL, so you can connect to localhost

4. Download the "LoginSystem.zip"  in our github.   https://github.com/yescolaa/Webpage-account-password-management-system/tree/main/src/php

5. Unzip the file and put the LoginSystem folder under ...\xampp\htdoc    My path look like this:   C:\xampp\htdocs

6. Download the "users.sql" file in our github.    <script src= "https://github.com/yescolaa/Webpage-account-password-management-system/tree/main/src/sql"</script>

7. Open up your browser and type:   http://localhost/phpmyadmin/index.php

8. Create a database naming "login_db". Find the import function and import "users.sql" into it.

9. Now use your browser go to   http://localhost/LoginSystem/login.php    and start using our System.
